name: hal 9000
tag_list: digital-marketing, online-marketing, seo, internet-marketing, ecommerce, web-marketing
overview:
Digital Marketing and Search Engine Optimisation Consultancy aimed at the start-up and SME sector.

Hal 9000 provides online marketing advice on how to grow your business online and offers a collaborative and sharing approach in creating an effective, and quantifiable, online marketing strategy.

Internet marketing and optimising for search engines, Google being by far the biggest player in the Irish market, is a fast-changing area and an online marketing strategy requires a different skill set to either traditional marketing (or offline marketing as it’s now called) or web design/development.
